{"tid":2262371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實BBA喺日常生活中都用唔到","createTime":"2020-10-29T05:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T09:38:42.000Z","uid":300420,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a32d14849a99c91a560a7fa6507c6488b50e26a8","tid":2262371,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"其實數學中二以上已經係日常生活中用唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2262039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2262039</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇完呢個Po有感而發 諗到樣比數學更加少日常生活應用嘅嘢 就係BBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀咗兩年呢個撚屌垃圾完全乜都學唔到 一推空泛嘅術語令到佢完全冇實用價值（係呀 數學對少數人有實用價值 但係BBA係冇 淨係可以幫教嗰個呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n更加重要嘅就BBA係連數學嘅美學價值都冇埋 完全就係一舊既冇實用價值 又冇理論基礎 更冇精神價值嘅學術垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔明點解每年仲有咁多傻仔仆去讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：BBA loser 讀商科讀到爛grade要靠CS/Math補救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024013dce34203c76b5e36fdfe05b711bdf0837d","tid":2262371,"uid":300918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a32d14849a99c91a560a7fa6507c6488b50e26a8","tid":2262371,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"其實數學中二以上已經係日常生活中用唔到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2262039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2262039</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇完呢個Po有感而發 諗到樣比數學更加少日常生活應用嘅嘢 就係BBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀咗兩年呢個撚屌垃圾完全乜都學唔到 一推空泛嘅術語令到佢完全冇實用價值（係呀 數學對少數人有實用價值 但係BBA係冇 淨係可以幫教嗰個呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.